 "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016403, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! You are Peace and the Peace is from You, O holder of dignity and honor, bless Mohammad and the progeny of Mohammad (s.a.w.a), and extend the best of greetings and blessings from me to them. O Allah these two units of prayers are dedicated from me to your servant and the son of your servant, your guardian and the son of your guardian, the son of your Prophet on earth and your proof on your entire creation, O guardian of believers, O guardian of believers, O guardian of believers.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ANTAS SALAAMO WA MIN-KAS SALAAMO, YAA ZAL-JALAALE WAL IKRAAME SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN TAYYE-BI-NAT TAAHE-REE-NAL AKH-YAARE, WA AB-LIGH-HUM MINNEE AFZA-LAT TAHIYYA-TE WAS-SALAAME. ALLAAHUMMA INNA HAA-TAIY-NIR RAK-A’TAIY-NE HADIYYA-TUN MINNEE ILAA A’BDE-KA WABNE A’BDE-KA WA WALIYYE-KA WABNE WALIYYE-KA SIBTE NABIYYE-KA FEE ARZE-KA WA HUJJATE-KA A’LAA KHALQE-KA, YAA WALIY-YAL MOA-MENEENA, YAA WALIY-YAL MOA-MENEENA, YAA WALIY-YAL MOA-MENEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْتَ السَّلَامُ وَمِنْكَ السَّلَامُ، یَا ذَالْجَلَالِ وَالْاِكْرَامِ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ الْاَخْیَارِ، وَاَبْلِغْهُمْ مِنِّیْ اَفْضَلَ التَّحِیَّۃِ وَالسَّلَامِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ هَاتَیْنِ الرَّكْعَتَیْنِ هَدِیَّۃٌ مِنِّیْ اِلٰی عَبْدِكَ وَابْنِ عَبْدِكَ وَ وَلِیِّكَ وَابْنِ وَلِیِّكَ سِبْطِ نَبِیِّكَ فِیْ اَرْضِكَ وَحُجَّتِكَ عَلٰی خَلْقِكَ، یَا وَلِیَّ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ، یَا وَلِیَّ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ، یَا وَلِیَّ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ۔", "ArabicG